Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.54,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You worked really well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:08.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.63,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You learn things fast and do them right, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You could be well-suited for this kind of job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Could it be... Are you complimenting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.98,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't get let it get to your head, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.67,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,We're doing the same thing every day,\Nso of course you'd improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:25.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:37.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All those people I studied with back then went to college and must be in some city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm not by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:47.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are people who get covered in dirt and grime every day like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:52.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's the new place I've chosen and have earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.33,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Now, here's a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Here he goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:35.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Which of the following is this summer's first big event I came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.06,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,One: BBQ at the Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.13,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Two: RIP at the Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Three: Barbara Fujioka at the Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They all sound so similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The last one was completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The "bar" sound is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You go play with Barbara Fujioka alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:51.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who is that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:55.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I haven't had a chance to play with Nagisa, so I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don't care what it is; I just want some time with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:06.11,San,San,0,0,0,,It's natural for you two to spend a lot of time together, but it's hard to let go of one's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.88,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.88,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}A Sudden Happening
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your place is really lively as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, there's something I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? You want a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's not that I don't want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:41.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right then. I get out early tomorrow, so let's go buy one tomorrow evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What? Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet you only have a school swimsuit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. But I don't mind that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After all, you want to see your girlfriend looking cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Be the beach queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What? Me in a swimsuit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't say that. We'll have fun shopping tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, then-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:22.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, have you met with\Nyour father properly after you've moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Have you told him your new address?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know that there's a distance between me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a distance that can never be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:37.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm working every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm working until I'm completely exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I want to be with you at least on my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't want to do anything unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:59.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's go meet him together one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,One day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. One day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:17.66,Default,Man,0,0,0,,My old colleague is working as an assistant director with the principal contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.41,Default,Man,0,0,0,,He's looking for a young person who can manage a site.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,First as a trainee,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.93,Default,Man,0,0,0,,but of course eventually as full staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:34.48,Default,Man,0,0,0,,They said they'll pay... about this much, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.31,Default,Man,0,0,0,,And I'm thinking of recommending you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.32,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Would you be interested in going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:48.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,W-Wait a moment please. Are you firing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.69,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:53.20,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He's recommending you because he cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.97,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to make a decision now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.70,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But I hope you would give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.71,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,What's there to hesitate over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:09.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I was thinking of building my career at this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Besides, you're more of an immediate help than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.77,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I'm bad at socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.88,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,I can be a technician but can't be a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.07,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You're younger, so you have more potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But this is too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.05,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If you take the offer, your pay will go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.11,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You'll eventually be supporting a family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.21,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:38.93,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,If there's someone important to you, then it's not too difficult to overcome several obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:45.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you start working here thinking things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That was a personal question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.63,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,You want to hear an old story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,A story of a boy who sang rock in this city before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.04,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He had done whatever he wanted since he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:12.82,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Nobody ever yelled at him,\Nso he was always doing bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.58,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Back then, the band scene was booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.86,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,So he picked up a guitar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:25.33,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Like running up on other people's stages and stealing the mike away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.00,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He was being ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.66,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,When he was a senior in high school, he met a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.31,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,She said she liked the love song he sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:44.48,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It had embarrassing lyrics,\Nbut she earnestly read the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Though, she was a clumsy one, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:55.12,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,she forgot she was in the middle of heading to class because she talked for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.67,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,After graduation, he was planning to live on music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:07.80,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everyone in class laughed at him, but that teacher encouraged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.43,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,She said, "As long as you continue, it will come true, so don't give up."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.36,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,On the day he left, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:21.43,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,"I'll definitely become a professional! If I do, please go out with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.96,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He etched in his heart that he would become a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.74,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The debut came pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.61,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,"Take that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.90,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He wanted to say that to all those who had made fun of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.81,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,From that day on, he worked frantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.28,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He sang what he wanted with everything he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:49.95,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Like spitting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.95,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Like vomiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.11,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,At times, he sang ugly lines, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:10.21,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But when he sang with everything he had, it sounded beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.30,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Living really felt refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:20.03,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Because to live was the ugliest act.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.71,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He had found his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.55,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,One day, a project was brought in from a TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.38,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It was to meet fans of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.80,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Not just any fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:45.33,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Fans that had been saved by his music and were still facing adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.76,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Those who were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.51,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Those who had gotten in accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.79,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Those who were going through tremendous hardship because of their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:58.27,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Those who had weak minds and were about to break down at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.83,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,They all stood in the midst of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.63,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,They all used his songs for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:17.14,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It was a moment he knew his song no longer belonged only to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:23.54,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Until that day, he had only sung for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.69,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But that was no longer true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:34.61,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He had to start composing for thousands of people he had never even met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.68,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He became unable to compose music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.27,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Because he had learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.10,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,...the grandeur of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.14,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,...his shallowness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.26,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,...and his insignificance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.69,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The agency told him to take a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.17,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,And six months later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.58,tv1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,764.1)\fad(900,0)}Year Old Arrested for Assault
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.58,tv2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\pos(1240.909,804.6)}Trouble between friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,A boy he had met through the TV program committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:09.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,A huge crime that couldn't be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.31,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everything fell apart from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.34,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The one who had committed the crime was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.60,tv3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1464.545,880.2)}Mysterious motive! Conflicting friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.86,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,...the one who said, "Listening to your songs calms my heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:29.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,"I want to hear your new song soon," the boy had said, speaking more enthusiastically than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:34.32,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He thought everything was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:41.24,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He thought he had taken away\Nthe boy's reason to live by not singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.64,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He started singing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:51.12,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He sang of the impossible and ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.80,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,thinking that would save those who waited for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:01.81,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He didn't have a clue why he was singing such words himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.43,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,But he continued to sing, ignoring the doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:13.29,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The songs eventually deviated from ideals and began to be echoes of a sick reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:17.54,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Only realistic pain could be attained from the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.13,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The lyrics didn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.01,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,They contradicted each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.80,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Even then, he continued to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,...because he feared the loss of singing the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:31.55,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.56,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He resorted to the worst choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.08,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It was an unforgivable mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.17,tv4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1680,837)\t(1600,2500,\c1&HFFFFFF&\3c1&HFFFFFF&)}Famous Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.17,tv5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414.545,688.5)\t(1600,2500,\c1&HFFFFFF&\3c1&HFFFFFF&)}Yoshino
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.17,tv5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578.182,688.5)\t(1600,2500,\c1&HFFFFFF&\3c1&HFFFFFF&)}Yusuke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.17,tv5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728.182,688.5)\t(1600,2500,\c1&HFFFFFF&\3c1&HFFFFFF&)}suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:47.11,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,No place was left for him after committing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:53.16,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,With nothing to rely on, in the depths of desperation, he made one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.62,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,"I want to go home."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.15,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Are you keeping up with music?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.71,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Everything had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.76,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,It couldn't have stayed the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:53.55,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,As long as you continue, it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.84,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,There was something he never should have lost sight of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.92,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,He should have continued singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.96,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Not for anyone else, but for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.50,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,The love songs for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.46,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Hey, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.89,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,That's the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.62,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:17.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.36,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:20.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.08,Yos,Yos,0,0,0,,Don't lose track of what's important to you. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:37.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think you should choose the path you think is best. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:38.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:43.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be transferred to another office, but you won't stop me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:48.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I won't, since it's proof that they've recognized how hard you've been working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.37,Default,Iso,0,0,0,,You won't play with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:10.01,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,You'd rather be with your girlfriend than play with children, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:14.26,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Really, look at how beautiful Nagisa-chan has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.06,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,You look just like me when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.21,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think you look kinder now, too. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:39.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You were talking with a smile to other people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Very naturally at that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:44.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I always thought things like that were annoying. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:48.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And I say this when at school, I stuck my nose into other people's business so much. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You don't feel that way now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:57.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,May I pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Please hold a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. It's from Hikarizaka Electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe the transfer went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello, Okazaki speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, good evening, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,From Kinoshita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. What's his phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They got a call from my pop's acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder what it could be about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.76,Default,Kin,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.85,Default,Kin,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoya-kun? We've got some trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:11.54,Default,Kin,0,0,0,,Your father got arrested by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.42,Default,Kin,0,0,0,,Apparently he was dealing with some dangerous stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.68,Default,Kin,0,0,0,,I heard the story and figured I had to get in contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:26.02,Default,Man,0,0,0,,It's a small city, so rumors spread fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:31.24,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Sorry, but they want to cancel the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:38.61,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But of course, continue to work here like you have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.84,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I guess things just happened at a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:45.87,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hold the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:51.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to leave this city together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I realized from this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm cursed by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I want to start over in a place where his curse won't reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's just running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't run away from something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want you to make me have a happy life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,...in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can make that happen away from this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You won't say that I'm all you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:32.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I would go anywhere if you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:38.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But we have to leave this city on a positive note if we are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:41.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Otherwise, this place won't become a place to come back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:47.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is the city in which we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if there's nothing good about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I had many good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:02.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The best is that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it fun ruining other people's lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't consider you my parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:34.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But society doesn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't even have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything to say to your son who you've caused so many problems for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop screwing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:59.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's enough. I've got nothing more to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Live like that forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:26.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Does your hand hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:11.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll sting when you get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:16.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:21.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:31.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:36.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've always been thinking that you're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm a guy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm a really pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:48.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But if we're together, we can become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will you always be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:58.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No matter when.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No matter how long.
